
What information do we collect?

During the use of this application you may be asked to fill in or select from a list a contact’s phone number to send text messages to. Your choice is not being sent or shared via internet, although it is being stored internally in the device’s memory. This data is not being backed up on line and has to be entered again if deleted from the device.

What do we use your information for?

The phone number you enter will be used to send text messages to, which may contain information about your location, speed and distance from your home location. None of this data is being shared with anyone by other means.

Do we disclose any information to outside parties?

The only party that receives your information is the one that the text messages are sent to during the use of this application, which is the one you specifically set by entering their phone number.

Your Consent

By using our app, you consent to our privacy policy.

Changes to our Privacy Policy

If we decide to change our privacy policy, we will post those changes or this page, and/or update the Privacy Policy modification date below.

This policy was last modified on 2 February 2017

Contacting Us

If there are any questions regarding this privacy policy you may contact us using the information below.

